[h1][img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SirDoggyJvla/Test/refs/heads/main/Images/Steam_Plumpabug.png[/img] Found a bug?[/h1]
You can report bugs on the GitHub issues page: [url=https://github.com/PZ-HorseTeam/HorseMod/issues]link[/url].

[h3]Known common issues:[/h3]
[list]
[*] MP is not supported yet, if you launch a save with it, you will get a pop up indicating it to you. ([url=https://github.com/PZ-HorseTeam/HorseMod/milestone/2]Milestone #2[/url])
[*] Equipments and manes on the horse have a large outline when aiming a weapon at it ([url=https://github.com/PZ-HorseTeam/HorseMod/issues/18]#18[/url])
[*] Aiming while riding a horse looks weird ([url=https://github.com/PZ-HorseTeam/HorseMod/issues/214]#214[/url])
[*] The horse animations don't load properly unless launching the game with the mod enabled from the start ([url=https://github.com/PZ-HorseTeam/HorseMod/issues/215]#215[/url])
[/list]

